WEBVTT

00:06:59.243 --> 00:07:00.761
what is on the record

00:07:00.785 --> 00:07:02.422
and off the record.

00:07:02.446 --> 00:07:04.980
I'm going to turn now to some NGO imagery

00:07:05.004 --> 00:07:08.271
which will be familiar
to some of you in this audience.

00:07:09.907 --> 00:07:13.147
(Video) Narrator: For about 70 cents,
you can buy a can of soda,

00:07:13.171 --> 00:07:14.488
regular or diet.

00:07:16.669 --> 00:07:19.655
In Ethiopia, for just 70 cents a day,

00:07:19.679 --> 00:07:23.351
you can feed a child like Jamal
nourishing meals.

00:07:24.159 --> 00:07:27.682
For about 70 cents,
you can also buy a cup of coffee.

00:07:28.572 --> 00:07:31.266
In Guatemala, for 70 cents a day,